0: SELECT MAX("Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)") FROM frpm WHERE "County Name" = 'Alameda';
1:
SELECT "School Name", "Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)"
FROM frpm
WHERE "School Type" = 'Continuation Schools'
ORDER BY "Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)" ASC
LIMIT 3;
2: SELECT "Zip" FROM schools WHERE "County" = 'Fresno' AND "Charter" = 1 AND "DOC" = 'Fresno County Office of Education';
3:
SELECT s."MailStreet" 
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY f."FRPM Count (K-12)" DESC
LIMIT 1;
4:
SELECT "Phone" 
FROM schools 
WHERE "Charter" = 1 
AND "FundingType" = 'Directly funded' 
AND "OpenDate" > '2000-01-01';
5:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM satscores
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode"
WHERE satscores."AvgScrMath" > 400 AND schools.Virtual = 'Y';
6:
SELECT s."School"
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores ss ON s."CDSCode" = ss.cds
WHERE ss."NumTstTakr" > 500 AND s."Magnet" = 1;
7:
SELECT sc."Phone" 
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools sc ON ss.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE ss."NumGE1500" = (SELECT MAX("NumGE1500") FROM satscores)
8:
SELECT "NumTstTakr" 
FROM satscores 
WHERE cds = (
    SELECT "CDSCode" 
    FROM frpm 
    ORDER BY "FRPM Count (K-12)" DESC 
    LIMIT 1
);
9:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores 
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode" 
WHERE satscores."AvgScrMath" > 560 
AND schools."Charter" = 1 
AND schools."FundingType" = 'Directly funded';
10:
SELECT f."FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)"
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
WHERE s."AvgScrRead" = (SELECT MAX("AvgScrRead") FROM satscores)
12:
SELECT MAX(f."Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)") 
FROM frpm f
JOIN satscores s ON f."CDSCode" = s.cds
WHERE (s."NumGE1500"::REAL / s."NumTstTakr") > 0.3;
13:
SELECT s."Phone"
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores ss ON s."CDSCode" = ss.cds
ORDER BY ss."NumGE1500" / ss."NumTstTakr" DESC
LIMIT 3;
14:
SELECT s."NCESSchool", f."School Name", f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)" DESC
LIMIT 5;
15:
SELECT s.dname 
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE sc."StatusType" = 'Active' AND s.rtype = 'D'
ORDER BY s."AvgScrRead" DESC 
LIMIT 1;
17:
SELECT s.sname, sc."CharterNum", ss."AvgScrWrite"
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools sc ON ss.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE ss."AvgScrWrite" > 499
ORDER BY ss."AvgScrWrite" DESC;
18:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores 
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode" 
WHERE schools."County" = 'Fresno' 
AND schools."FundingType" = 'Directly funded' 
AND satscores."NumTstTakr" <= 250;
19:
SELECT sc."Phone" 
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools sc ON ss.cds = sc."CDSCode"
ORDER BY ss."AvgScrMath" DESC 
LIMIT 1;
21:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM frpm 
WHERE "County Name" = 'Los Angeles' 
AND "Free Meal Count (K-12)" > 500 
AND "FRPM Count (K-12)" < 700;
22:
SELECT "sname" 
FROM "satscores" 
WHERE "cname" = 'Contra Costa' 
ORDER BY "NumTstTakr" DESC 
LIMIT 1;
23:
SELECT s."School", s."Street", s."City", s."Zip", s."State"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
WHERE ABS(f."Enrollment (K-12)" - f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)") > 30;
24:
SELECT f."School Name"
FROM frpm f
JOIN satscores s ON f."CDSCode" = s.cds
WHERE f."Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)" > 0.1
AND s."NumGE1500" > 0;
25:
SELECT s."School", sc."FundingType"
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
JOIN frpm sc ON s."CDSCode" = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE s."County" = 'Riverside'
GROUP BY s."School", sc."FundingType"
HAVING AVG(ss."AvgScrMath") > 400;
26:
SELECT s."School", s."Street", s."City", s."Zip", s."State"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
WHERE f."County Name" = 'Monterey'
AND f."High Grade" = '12'
AND f."Low Grade" <= '9'
AND f."FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)" > 800;
27:
SELECT 
    s."School" AS school_name, 
    sat."AvgScrWrite" AS average_writing_score, 
    s."Phone" AS communication_number
FROM 
    schools s
JOIN 
    satscores sat ON s."CDSCode" = sat.cds
WHERE 
    (s."OpenDate" > '1991-12-31' OR s."ClosedDate" < '2000-01-01')
28:
WITH EnrollmentDifference AS (
    SELECT 
        s."School" AS SchoolName,
        s."DOCType",
        (f."Enrollment (K-12)" - f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)") AS EnrollmentDiff
    FROM 
        frpm f
    JOIN 
        schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
    WHERE 
        s."FundingType" = 'Locally funded'
),
AverageDifference AS (
    SELECT AVG(EnrollmentDiff) AS AvgDiff
    FROM EnrollmentDifference
)
SELECT 
    SchoolName,
    "DOCType"
FROM 
    EnrollmentDifference
WHERE 
    EnrollmentDiff > (SELECT AvgDiff FROM AverageDifference);
29:
SELECT "OpenDate" 
FROM schools 
WHERE "CDSCode" = (
    SELECT "CDSCode" 
    FROM frpm 
    WHERE "Low Grade" = '1' AND "High Grade" = '12' 
    ORDER BY "Enrollment (K-12)" DESC 
    LIMIT 1
);
30:
SELECT "City" 
FROM schools 
JOIN frpm ON schools."CDSCode" = frpm."CDSCode" 
WHERE frpm."Low Grade" <= '1' AND frpm."High Grade" >= '12' 
ORDER BY frpm."Enrollment (K-12)" ASC 
LIMIT 5;
31:
SELECT "Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)" 
FROM frpm 
ORDER BY "Enrollment (K-12)" DESC 
LIMIT 2 OFFSET 9;
32:
SELECT "School Name", "Percent (%) Eligible FRPM (K-12)"
FROM frpm
JOIN schools ON frpm."CDSCode" = schools."CDSCode"
WHERE schools."SOC" = '66' AND frpm."Low Grade" <= '1' AND frpm."High Grade" >= '12'
ORDER BY "FRPM Count (K-12)" DESC
LIMIT 5;
33:
SELECT s."School", s."Website"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
WHERE f."Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)" BETWEEN 1900 AND 2000;
34:

FROM frpm 
JOIN schools ON frpm."CDSCode" = schools."CDSCode" 
WHERE schools."AdmFName1" = 'Kacey' AND schools."AdmLName1" = 'Gibson';
35:

FROM schools 
WHERE "Charter" = 1

LIMIT 1;
36:

FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY ss."NumGE1500" DESC
LIMIT 1;
37:
SELECT "Street", "City", "Zip", "State" 
FROM schools 
WHERE "CDSCode" = (
    SELECT "CDSCode" 
    FROM frpm 
    ORDER BY "Percent (%) Eligible FRPM (K-12)" ASC 
    LIMIT 1

38:
SELECT "Website" 
FROM schools 
JOIN satscores ON schools."CDSCode" = satscores.cds 
WHERE satscores.cname = 'Los Angeles' 
AND satscores."NumTstTakr" BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000;
39:
SELECT AVG(satscores."NumTstTakr") 
FROM satscores 
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode" 
WHERE schools.County = 'Fresno' 
AND schools.OpenDate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1980-12-31';
